\v 12 \add вүҲButВҰ167631 she replied\add*, вҖңAs your godВҰ167635 YahwehВҰ167634 \add вүҲlives, I don't have any bread atВҰ167649 all\add*вҖ”only a \add вүҲhandful\add* of flourВҰ167648 in the jar, and a little bit of oilВҰ167652 in the jug. See, I'm gatheringВҰ167655 \add вүҲa few bits of firewood so I can make a little bread\add* for me and my son. \add вүҲAfter we've eaten that\add*, thenВҰ167631 we'll dieВҰ167663.вҖқ
