\v 15 \add вүҲSoВҰ167717 the woman wentВҰ167717 and did what Eliyah said\add*, thenВҰ167717 \add sure enough\add* \add @Eliyah\add* and \add @the widow\add* and herВҰ167726 householdВҰ167726 \add вүҲhad enough food every day\add*.
\v 16 The jar of flourВҰ167730 \add вүҲnever got empty\add* and the jug of oilВҰ167734 \add вүҲnever ran out, just as YahwehВҰ167738 had promised via\add* EliyahВҰ167742.
