\p
\v 17 \add вүҲSome time afterwardsВҰ167746,\add* the woman'sВҰ167752 son got sickВҰ167749 and then \add вүҲit got so bad that he died\add*,
\v 18 \add вүҲso\add* she hassled EliyahВҰ167771, вҖңYou manВҰ167776 of God, \add вүҲwhy did you comeВҰ167778 here! Now my sins have been brought to God's mind, andВҰ167768 he's causedВҰ167784 my son to die!\add*вҖқ
