\v 19 \add вүҲButВҰ167794 he told her to bring her son to him, and taking the boy from her arms, he tookВҰ167797 the body upstairsВҰ167802 to the roomВҰ167802 he was stayingВҰ167806 in\add*, and laid him down on his bed.
