\p
\v 1 \add вүҲIn the thirdВҰ167919 yearВҰ167918 of drought, YahwehВҰ167913 told EliyahВҰ167917 to goВҰ167921 and show himself to King Ahav and tell him that it would soon\add* rain,
\v 2 \add вүҲso he wentВҰ167933 to presentВҰ167935 himself\add* to Ahav.
