\v 5 \add King\add* Ahav told Ovadyah, вҖң\add We'll\add* goВҰ167983 \add вүҲacross the country\add* to all the springsВҰ167989 and all the \add вүҲvalleysВҰ167994 that waterВҰ167990 sometimes flows in\add*. Perhaps we'll find \add some\add* grassВҰ167998 \add вүҲso\add* we can keepВҰ167999 a horseВҰ168000 or a mule \add or two\add* aliveВҰ167999 and not \add вүҲlose our breeding stock\add*.вҖқ
\v 6 \add вүҲSoВҰ168008\add* they dividedВҰ168006 the country \add into two\add*, andВҰ168006 \add вүҲthey each went off inВҰ168013 a different direction\add*.
