\v 7 \add вүҲWhile\add* Ovadyah was onВҰ168028 a pathВҰ168028, Eliyah \add came to\add* meet him. \add @Ovadyah\add* recognisedВҰ168032 him and fell \add вүҲto his knees withВҰ168028 his face to the ground, and asked\add*, вҖңIs it \add really\add* you, my masterВҰ168040 Eliyah?вҖқ
