\v 9 вҖңHow have I sinnedВҰ168054,вҖқ Ovadyah \add вүҲrespondedВҰ168052\add*, вҖңthat you'reВҰ168057 givingВҰ168058 yourВҰ168061 servantВҰ168061 \add вүҲa death sentence\add*?
