\v 12 \add вүҲbutВҰ168106\add* as soon as I leave you, Yahweh's spiritВҰ168111 will take you to \add вүҲgoodness knows whereВҰ168116\add*. \add вүҲMeanwhile\add* I'llВҰ168109 goВҰ168109 and tell Ahav, and he'll comeВҰ168120 here and not find you, \add вүҲso\add* thenВҰ168106 he'll killВҰ168125 me, \add вүҲeven though I've been trying to obey Yahweh since I was young\add*.
