\p
\v 19 \add вүҲSoВҰ169194\add* \add @Eliyah\add* left that place and wentВҰ169194 and foundВҰ169196 Shafat'sВҰ169202 son ElishaВҰ169199. \add вүҲThere were twelve teams ploughing a field and he was withВҰ169211 the back pair\add* \add of cattle\add*. Eliyah \add walked\add* past him and threwВҰ169216 hisВҰ169209 cloak over him.
\v 20 \add @Elisha\add* left \add вүҲthe plough\add* and ranВҰ169224 after EliyahВҰ169226, saying, вҖңPlease let me kissВҰ169228 my fatherВҰ169231 and my motherВҰ169232, then \add вүҲI'll come with\add* you.вҖқ
\p вҖңGo \add вүҲon back then\add*,вҖқ \add @Eliyah\add* \add вүҲreplied\add*, вҖң\add вүҲbecause I haven't done anything for\add* you.вҖқ
\p
\v 21 \add вүҲSoВҰ169245\add* \add @Elisha\add* wentВҰ169261 back and killed his pair of cattle. He \add вүҲused the wood of the plough to cook the meat onВҰ169253, and he shared it around\add* the peopleВҰ169258. \add вүҲAfter they'd eaten, he packed up and followedВҰ169246 EliyahВҰ169263 and became his helper\add*.
\c 20
\s1 Ben-Hadad attacks Shomron
