\p
\v 1 \add At that time,\add* KingВҰ169270 Ben-Hadam of AramВҰ169272 \add (SyriaВҰ169272)\add* \add вүҲjoined withВҰ169291 thirty-two smaller kingdoms and they brought their combined armies and horsesВҰ169283 and chariotsВҰ169284\add* and besieged Yisrael's capital ShomronВҰ169289 \add (Samaria) ready\add* to attack it.
\v 2 He sentВҰ169293 messengersВҰ169294 to Yisrael'sВҰ169300 KingВҰ169298 Ahav \add who was inside\add* the cityВҰ169301
\v 3 to tell him, вҖңBenВҰ169307-HadadВҰ169309 saysВҰ169306 that your goldВҰ169312 and silverВҰ169311 are mine, as well as the best of your wivesВҰ169316 and sons.вҖқ
