\v 4 вҖң\add вүҲWhatever you say\add*, my masterВҰ169329 the king,вҖқ replied Yisrael'sВҰ169326 king. вҖң\add вүҲI'm yoursВҰ169331 along with everything I have\add*.вҖқ
