\v 5 ThenВҰ169339 the messengersВҰ169340 returnedВҰ169339, saying, вҖңBenВҰ169345-HadadВҰ169347 saidВҰ169341 that you'll giveВҰ169359 him your goldВҰ169355 and silverВҰ169354 and your wivesВҰ169356 and sons,
\v 6 butВҰ169372 around this time tomorrowВҰ169366, he'll send his servants to you to searchВҰ169372 through your \add вүҲpalace\add* and the homes of your \add вүҲpeople\add*, and they'll take \add вүҲeverythingВҰ169380 that they consider to be of value\add*.вҖқ
\p
\v 7 \add вүҲSoВҰ169388\add* Yisrael's king \add вүҲsummoned\add* all Yisrael's leaders and told them, вҖң\add вүҲListen and note how this man is lookingВҰ169404 forВҰ169404 troubleВҰ169402. He's claiming my wivesВҰ169409 and my sons, and my goldВҰ169412 and silverВҰ169411, and I didn'tВҰ169413 contradict\add* him.вҖқ
