\v 8 \add вүҲButВҰ169417\add* the eldersВҰ169421 and all the others \add вүҲrespondedВҰ169417\add*, вҖң\add No,\add* don't listenВҰ169427 \add to him\add* and don't consent \add to his demands\add*.вҖқ
