\p
\v 13 \add вүҲJust thenВҰ169516,\add*, a prophetВҰ169518 \add вүҲapproached\add* Yisrael'sВҰ169526 KingВҰ169524 Ahav andВҰ169516 told \add >him\add*, вҖңYahweh \add вүҲasks if you've seenВҰ169531 that greatВҰ169536 army, because he's going to giveВҰ169539 you victory over them today so you'll knowВҰ169542 that Yahweh is God\add*.вҖқ
