\v 14 вҖң\add вүҲWho will enable the victory\add*?вҖқ Ahav \add вүҲasked\add*.
\p вҖңYahwehВҰ169555 saysВҰ169554 \add it'll be\add* the youngВҰ169556 menВҰ169556 under the provincialВҰ169558 commanders,вҖқ he \add вүҲanswered\add*.
